There were two deaths (one in each group) reported at the data cutoff, neither of which was considered related to the study treatments. Interpretation In this interim analysis, ZyCoV-D vaccine was found to be efficacious, safe, and immunogenic in a phase 3 trial. Funding National Biopharma Mission, Department of Biotechnology, Government of India and Cadila Healthcare, Ahmedabad, Gujarat India.
