Risks for Anaphylaxis With Intravenous Iron Formulations : A Retrospective Cohort Study.
 The rates of anaphylaxis were very low with al IV iron products but were 3- to 8-fold greater for iron dextran and ferumoxytol than for iron sucrose. Primary funding source None.
